<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When there is no error, Zend_Json_Server_Response will not return it, however in the JSON-RPC specification if there is no error it must be returned as null.</p>

<p><a href="http://json-rpc.org/wiki/specification#a1.2Response">http://json-rpc.org/wiki/specification/…</a></p>

